        <section id="activity3" class="slide flex flex-col items-center justify-center">
            <div class="w-full max-w-5xl bg-white p-10 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-slate-200">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-blue-600 mb-2">Activity 3: Cup-Stacking BSTs</h2>
                <p class="text-center text-slate-500 mb-8">(25 minutes)</p>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-2xl mb-4">The Golden Rule</h3>
                        <div class="bg-amber-100 border-l-4 border-amber-500 text-amber-800 p-4 rounded-r-lg">
                           <p>Start at the root. If the new number is <span class="font-bold">LESS THAN</span> the node, go <span class="font-bold">LEFT</span>.</p>
                           <p>If it's <span class="font-bold">GREATER THAN</span>, go <span class="font-bold">RIGHT</span>.</p>
                           <p>Repeat until you find an empty spot!</p>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-2xl mt-6 mb-4">Let's Build!</h3>
                        <p>In your groups, add these numbers one by one using your cups:</p>
                        <div class="mt-2 text-2xl font-mono bg-slate-100 p-4 rounded-lg text-center">
                            [ 50, 30, 70, 20, 40, 80 ]
                        </div>
                    </div>
